1. Instalasi CentOS 7 Server 
   - Setting TimeZone -> Asia-Jakarta
   - Server Selection -> Minimal Install
   - Partition  : /boot    -> 2048 MiB
                : biosboot -> automatic (2048KiB)
                : swap     -> 4GiB (Better 2x Ram)
                : /        -> sisanya 
   - Setting Root Password
1.1 Instalation CentOS 7 Server (Raid)
   - Setting TimeZone -> Asia-Jakarta
   - Server Selection -> Minimal Install
   - Pilih hardisk dengan kapasitas yang sama
   - Partition : /boot -> 1024 MiB
               : swap  -> 2048 MiB (Better 2x Ram)
               : /     -> Device Type : Raid
                       -> Raid Level  : Raid 1 (Redudancy)
                       -> File System : Xfs
                       -> Label : mdo
                       -> Name  : root
   - Setting Root Password
